snippet.title: Aim Lab - The free aim trainer you know you need
snippet.description:
Blending cutting-edge performance, tracking, and analytics with artificial intelligence to make you better, faster. Bad at flick shots to your left? Can’t hit strafing or jumping targets? We fix that. Our rich data visualizations help you understand your performance and let you level up in no time! 

Steam ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/71...
